Unified Ambulance Emergency System — Full Agent Prompt

Scope: This prompt covers the complete system — Client App, Admin Dashboard, and Driver App — as a single synchronized platform.


System Overview
An Ambulance Emergency Booking System with three interconnected surfaces:
SurfaceUsersPurposeClient AppPatients (public)Request ambulances, track in real-timeAdmin DashboardCompany admins / Super AdminsManage ambulances, drivers, bookings, paymentsDriver AppRegistered driversReceive requests, accept/deny, navigate to patient
