9. Key Design Principles

No generic dispatch labels — always show Company + Driver Name + ID
One login, smart routing — role detected server-side, redirect client-side
Driver flow mirrors SafeBoda — full-screen incoming request, accept/deny with timeout
Everything syncs — booking state changes propagate instantly to all three surfaces via Socket.io rooms
Public client — zero friction for patients in emergencies
Secure admin/driver — RBAC-protected, JWT + refresh tokens


